wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/marilyn-manson">玛丽莲·曼森 (Marilyn Manson)</a>不会在 2019 年涉嫌向一名摄像师吐口水和擤鼻涕的案件中提出抗辩。</p><p>曼森的真名是布莱恩·华纳 (Brian Warner)，被摄像师苏珊·方丹 (Susan Fountain) 指控，2019 年 8 月 19 日，曼森在新罕布什尔州吉尔福德为他的演唱会拍摄时，向她吐了一口“大卢基”并向她擤鼻涕。</p><p>这位摇滚歌手被指控犯有两项轻罪，即简单袭击事件。这一认罪将使他能够避免原定于下个月开始的审判。</p><p>据<em><a href="https://apnews.com/article/marilyn-manson-nose-spit-f3db1fa62004495f2fa9b37e9a85aac9" target="_blank" rel="noopener">美联社</a></em>报道，如果这位歌手接受审判并被定罪，他将面临监禁和每项指控 2000 美元（1554 英镑）的罚款。</p><p>如果法官接受曼森的认罪（预计周四将在贝尔纳普县高等法院提交），他将必须支付 1200 美元（933 英镑）的罚款，并因擤鼻涕的罪行接受 20 小时的社区服务，同时涉及吐痰事件的指控将被撤销。 </p><figure id="attachment_3471228" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3471228" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3471228" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring.jpg" alt="玛丽莲·曼森于 2020 年 1 月 4 日出席极乐世界艺术第 13 届年度庆典 - 天堂。图片来源：Leon Bennett/GETTY" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Marilyn-manson-staring-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3471228" class="wp-caption-text">玛丽莲·曼森于 2020 年 1 月 4 日出席极乐世界艺术第 13 届年度庆典——天堂。图片来源：Leon Bennett/GETTY</figcaption></figure><p>曼森最近面临<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-and-other-women-make-allegations-of-abuse-against-marilyn-manson-2869492">着十几名女性提出的各种诉讼和指控，</a>指控他性虐待和身体虐待。受到指控后，这位创作歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-dropped-by-record-label-amid-abuse-allegations-2869945">被他的唱片公司 Loma Vista 解雇</a>。</p><p>其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/westworld"><em>《西部世界》</em></a>演员埃文·雷切尔·伍德 (Evan Rachel Wood)，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/evan-rachel-wood-and-other-women-make-allegations-of-abuse-against-marilyn-manson-2869492">早在 2022 年就指控曼森诱骗、操纵和“可怕的虐待行为”</a> 。</p><p>同年3月，曼森<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-sues-evan-rachel-wood-for-defamation-3173472">对伍德提起诽谤诉讼</a>。然而上周（5 月 10 日），一位美国法官<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-defamation-case-against-evan-rachel-wood-mostly-dismissed-by-us-judge-3441811">驳回了这位音乐家案件的关键部分</a>。其中包括声称伍德向“多名女性施压，要求他们对他提出虚假指控”，并捏造了一封联邦调查局的信来支持她的指控（来自<a href="https://www.latimes.com/entertainment-arts/music/story/2023-05-09/marilyn-manson-evan-rachel-wood-lawsuit-defamation" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《洛杉矶时报》</em></a> ）。</p><p>另一项指控来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/game-of-thrones"><em>《权力的游戏》</em></a>演员埃斯梅·比安科，他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/game-of-thrones-actress-esme-bianco-accuses-marilyn-manson-of-abuse-i-felt-like-a-prisoner-2877873">声称他们的关系包括毒品</a>、持续监控、身体虐待和性侵犯。该<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/games-of-thrones-actor-esme-bianco-and-marilyn-manson-reach-settlement-in-sexual-assault-lawsuit-3386310">诉讼后来于今年一月达成和解</a>。</p><p>目前，这位“Dope Show”歌手还面临着另外两起诉讼，均由简·杜斯提起。他一贯<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-denies-abuse-allegations-calls-recent-claims-horrible-distortions-of-reality-2870187">否认所有指控</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/marilyn-manson-to-plead-no-contest-in-spitting-and-nose-blowing-assault-case-3471223">玛丽